                    Get 25% off on all summer collection items. Applicable on
                    orders above ₹1000.
                  </p>
                  <div class="flex items-center mt-2 text-xs text-gray-500">
                    <i class="far fa-clock mr-1"></i>
                    <span
                      >Valid till:
                      <span class="font-medium">June 30, 2025</span></span
                    >
